N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4206.2 - Passes

State Regulations

No track licensee shall issue any pass card or badge
entitling any person to free admission to its track, except in accordance with
section 83 of chapter 1023 of the Laws of 1970. Notes
